Class AddSubSequence

java.lang.Object
  sequence.processor.command.Command

All Implemented Interfaces:
ICommand
public class AddSubSequence
extends Command

The command that is used to add a sub sequence from a summarized sequence. A sequence container containing a sub sequence view instanciated with the sequence will be added to the parent of the summarized sequence.
